### =============================================================
### BOOKSHARE API - TESTES DE PROTEÇÃO DE ROTAS (GUARDS)
### =============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3002

### 1. Testar GET /users/:id sem token (Esperado: 401 Unauthorized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Testar GET /users/:id/profile sem token (Esperado: 401 Unauthorized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/profile
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 3. Testar POST /books sem token (Esperado: 401 Unauthorized)
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "titulo": "Hackers",
  "autor": "Steven Levy",
  "isbn": "99999",
  "donoId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

###

### 4. Testar POST /loans sem token (Esperado: 401 Unauthorized)
POST {{baseUrl}}/loans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "livroId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

###

### 5. Testar PUT /loans/:id/approve sem token (Esperado: 401 Unauthorized)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/loans/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/approve
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 6. Testar PUT /loans/:id/return sem token (Esperado: 401 Unauthorized)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/loans/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/return
Content-Type: application/json
